flowchart TD
    A[🇮🇳 Customer selects UPI] --> B{Payment Type}

    B -->|One-time| C[UPI Collect Request]
    B -->|Recurring| D[e-Mandate Registration\nRBI Mandate]
    B -->|Intent / QR| E[UPI Intent / QR Code]

    C --> F[Enter UPI ID\ne.g. user@upibank]
    F --> G[Payment Gateway sends\ncollect request to NPCI]
    G --> H[NPCI routes to\ncustomer PSP bank]
    H --> I[Push notification\non customer UPI app]
    I --> J{Customer approves\n& enters UPI PIN?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Bank debits account]
    J -->|No / Timeout| L[❌ Payment failed\nor expired]
    J -->|Declined| L

    K --> M[NPCI confirms to\npayment gateway]
    M --> N[✅ Payment confirmed\ninstantly]

    D --> O[Collect mandate details:\nAmount, frequency, validity]
    O --> P[Customer approves mandate\nvia UPI PIN]
    P --> Q{RBI e-Mandate Rules}
    Q --> R[Auto-debit ≤ ₹15,000:\nNo pre-notification needed]
    Q --> S[Auto-debit > ₹15,000:\n24hr pre-notification +\ncustomer approval each time]
    R --> T[Scheduled auto-debit\nvia NPCI]
    S --> U[Send pre-debit\nnotification]
    U --> V{Customer approves?}
    V -->|Yes| T
    V -->|No| W[❌ Debit blocked\nby customer]
    T --> N

    E --> X[Generate UPI\ndeep link or QR]
    X --> Y[Customer scans QR\nor opens in UPI app]
    Y --> Z[Customer enters\nUPI PIN in own app]
    Z --> K

    N --> AA{Regulatory\nCompliance}
    AA --> AB[₹2 lakh per\ntransaction limit]
    AA --> AC[TCS 1% on overseas\nremittances > ₹7 lakh/year]
    AA --> AD[GSTIN required for\nB2B > ₹50,000]

    style A fill:#4A90D9,color:#fff
    style N fill:#7ED321,color:#fff
    style L fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style W fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style Q fill:#F5A623,color:#fff
